###The main intention of the Rental Bond Tracker is to ensure that the tenants have a unified, secure 
and easy-to-use system to administer the information of the rental bond and the documentation 
of tenancies. This platform aims to eradicate the manual record keeping inefficiencies by 
providing an orderly system of managing bond payments, storing lease agreements, and 
insurance of inspection records by tenants. This project will help to minimize bond disputes, 
enhance tenant confidence and enable quicker and simpler bond refunds by ensuring that 
important tenancy documentation is digitized, centrally located and readily available. The system 
is meant to enhance better organization of records, less administrative load on tenants and 
enhance predictability of bond outcome.
